        "heading": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Every piece of Efemera jewelry is designed as a small sculpture.",
            "heading_tag": "h2",
            "heading_font_class": "fs-heading-1-base"
          }
        },
        "text": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We favor asymmetry, subtle tension, and forms that feel alive rather than static. Every curve and edge serves a deliberate purpose — nothing is accidental, yet nothing feels forced.</p><p>Each piece is designed with intention. From the materials, to the emotions and meaning. We believe beauty is not only in the sparkle of gold or pearls, but in the story each piece comes to hold for the one who wears it.</p>",
            "text_font_class": "fs-body-100"
          }
        },
